1
00:00:35,150 --> 00:00:36,840
In the years gone by,

2
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:38,430
the arts programs on the radio

3
00:00:38,430 --> 00:00:39,640
once brought

4
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:41,030
a lot of joy to the audience.

5
00:00:41,840 --> 00:00:42,920
Today, the arts channel

6
00:00:43,350 --> 00:00:45,070
will provide you

7
00:00:45,070 --> 00:00:47,390
with more and better programs.

8
00:00:47,750 --> 00:00:49,200
This also fulfills

9
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:51,920
the decades-long dream
of the older generation

10
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:52,840
of radio arts workers.

11
00:00:54,350 --> 00:00:55,600
Speaking of fulfilling dreams,

12
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:57,000
I'm reminded of someone

13
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:59,470
and a true story.

14
00:00:59,470 --> 00:01:01,240
It happened right here,

15
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:03,600
and it's not far from us at all.

16
00:03:03,980 --> 00:03:11,260
=Eight Hundred=

17
00:03:17,460 --> 00:03:23,820
(Year 1997, Fengyang Town, Jiangbin City)

18
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:30,650
♪Perhaps everything
has slowly passed us by♪

19
00:03:31,860 --> 00:03:33,700
Fengyang

20
00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:35,940
has produced coal since the Jiaqing era.

21
00:03:35,940 --> 00:03:37,700
But the quality isn't good.

22
00:03:37,700 --> 00:03:38,700
It doesn't burn well.

23
00:03:38,700 --> 00:03:40,860
(Provide more coals. Make more contributions)
You can dig for a whole day,

24
00:03:40,860 --> 00:03:42,180
and it still won't sell for much.

25
00:03:42,580 --> 00:03:44,020
Back when the country
was liberated,

26
00:03:44,020 --> 00:03:47,300
there were only about
thirty households in this town.

27
00:03:47,300 --> 00:03:48,260
But look at it now.

28
00:03:48,260 --> 00:03:49,860
(National Fitness Activity)
It has grown to cover

29
00:03:49,860 --> 00:03:51,380
an 800-meter radius area

30
00:03:51,380 --> 00:03:52,900
with thousands of households.

31
00:03:54,860 --> 00:03:56,340
Those years

32
00:03:56,940 --> 00:03:58,980
were difficult times.

33
00:03:58,980 --> 00:04:01,100
National resources were scarce.

34
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,780
It was under those circumstances

35
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:05,340
that the Fengyang Coal Mine
was established.

36
00:04:05,340 --> 00:04:06,190
Suddenly,

37
00:04:06,190 --> 00:04:09,780
thousands of people poured in
from all over the country.

38
00:04:10,460 --> 00:04:11,360
That's right.

39
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:13,620
Hongbing, back then
your father and my father

40
00:04:13,740 --> 00:04:15,540
were part of them.

41
00:04:16,180 --> 00:04:19,420
I remember when our fathers arrived,
they were only in their early twenties.

42
00:04:19,420 --> 00:04:21,220
They were all young men.

43
00:04:21,220 --> 00:04:22,900
Liang, it took two generations.

44
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:24,300
- Two whole generations.
- Exactly.

45
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:25,700
With their unremitting efforts,

46
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:26,980
they finally built

47
00:04:26,980 --> 00:04:29,020
"Little Hong Kong, China" in the valley

48
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:30,260
within an 800-meter radius.

49
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:31,960
See how prosperous

50
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:33,330
our place is.

51
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,490
Right?

52
00:04:34,490 --> 00:04:35,490
Come on.

53
00:04:35,490 --> 00:04:36,800
Director Liao, let me give you a toast.

54
00:04:37,380 --> 00:04:38,220
Liang,

55
00:04:38,540 --> 00:04:39,420
let me use your phone.

56
00:04:41,180 --> 00:04:42,020
Here.

57
00:04:50,820 --> 00:04:51,700
Hello?

58
00:04:51,700 --> 00:04:52,620
What's the matter?

59
00:04:52,620 --> 00:04:55,220
Master, something happened
at the Beimianling coal gangue dump.

60
00:04:55,730 --> 00:04:56,580
Fine,

61
00:04:56,580 --> 00:04:57,700
I'll head over right now.

62
00:05:00,140 --> 00:05:00,980
Pay attention!

63
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:01,980
Protect the scene.

64
00:05:01,980 --> 00:05:03,760
- Limin!
- Put up two more tape lines there.

65
00:05:04,110 --> 00:05:04,950
Master.

66
00:05:06,020 --> 00:05:06,940
What's the situation?

67
00:05:06,940 --> 00:05:09,900
We received a report from a villager
who saw a fire at Beimianling.

68
00:05:09,900 --> 00:05:11,100
They called the police,

69
00:05:11,100 --> 00:05:12,940
and a body was found
after the fire was out.

70
00:05:12,940 --> 00:05:14,020
So they notified us.

71
00:05:14,020 --> 00:05:15,000
We preliminarily suspect

72
00:05:15,010 --> 00:05:16,340
it was a spontaneous combustion
of the coal gangue.

73
00:05:16,340 --> 00:05:18,140
Coal gangue?

74
00:05:18,140 --> 00:05:19,100
Did you notify the municipal PSB?

75
00:05:19,100 --> 00:05:20,340
Director Tong was calling when I came.

76
00:05:20,340 --> 00:05:21,780
- Director Tong.
- Okay, thanks.

77
00:05:21,780 --> 00:05:23,020
- Han.
- Hello, Director Chen.

78
00:05:23,020 --> 00:05:24,300
Let us borrow your tent

79
00:05:24,300 --> 00:05:25,220
and some caution tape.

80
00:05:25,220 --> 00:05:26,060
What's wrong?

81
00:05:26,070 --> 00:05:26,940
Is it bankrupt?

82
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:28,860
Don't always divide things
into yours and mine.

83
00:05:28,860 --> 00:05:29,820
Well, you have a gun too.

84
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:30,660
Does that count as mine?

85
00:05:30,660 --> 00:05:31,660
If I give you a gun,
will you fight the fire with it?

86
00:05:31,660 --> 00:05:32,900
I wouldn't dare.

87
00:05:32,900 --> 00:05:34,100
- Come on.
- Shao,

88
00:05:34,100 --> 00:05:35,180
bring that tent over here

89
00:05:35,180 --> 00:05:36,660
- and ten more meters of caution tape.
- Yes.

90
00:05:36,660 --> 00:05:37,580
Twenty meters.

91
00:05:37,580 --> 00:05:39,220
Fine, give him everything in the car.

92
00:05:39,220 --> 00:05:40,740
Let him wrap Fengyang in a circle.

93
00:05:40,740 --> 00:05:41,700
Look,

94
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:42,660
it's completely charred.

95
00:06:18,460 --> 00:06:19,900
It's a coin.

96
00:06:20,740 --> 00:06:22,820
It's a commemorative coin
for the Year of the Ox.

97
00:06:23,740 --> 00:06:25,700
Someone stay here tonight
to keep watch with me.

98
00:06:25,700 --> 00:06:27,100
Limin, go and check

99
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:28,540
if anyone is missing.

100
00:06:55,020 --> 00:06:59,420
(Year 1972)

101
00:06:59,420 --> 00:07:01,460
(The female corpse
is clearly charred.)

102
00:07:22,060 --> 00:07:26,020
=Episode 1=
(Burning)

103
00:07:40,300 --> 00:07:41,210
Hey!

104
00:07:41,460 --> 00:07:42,300
What are you doing?

105
00:07:43,420 --> 00:07:44,580
I'm talking to you.

106
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,350
I'm Liu Na from the municipal PSB.

107
00:07:51,580 --> 00:07:52,500
Hello,

108
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:54,510
I'm Chen Hongbing from
the Fengyang Police Station,

109
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:56,460
the Deputy Director
in charge of public security.

110
00:07:56,460 --> 00:07:57,540
Hello.

111
00:07:57,540 --> 00:07:58,590
- Hello.
- Tang Yimei, Technical Detachment.

112
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,530
Just call me Yimei.

113
00:07:59,540 --> 00:08:00,580
Hello.

114
00:08:00,580 --> 00:08:01,500
Let's see the scene.

115
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:02,380
This way, please.

116
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,180
The body hasn't been moved, right?

117
00:08:08,180 --> 00:08:09,020
No.

118
00:08:09,020 --> 00:08:10,360
I've been watching over it all night.

119
00:08:11,860 --> 00:08:12,700
By the way,

120
00:08:13,260 --> 00:08:14,300
right next to the body,

121
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:15,280
I also picked up

122
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:16,140
a commemorative coin.

123
00:08:16,140 --> 00:08:18,660
The director of
the local savings office said

124
00:08:18,660 --> 00:08:20,220
there are

125
00:08:20,220 --> 00:08:21,460
two coins in a set.

126
00:08:21,460 --> 00:08:23,220
One has a yellow ring and white core,

127
00:08:23,220 --> 00:08:24,980
and the other has
a white ring and yellow core.

128
00:08:24,980 --> 00:08:26,460
If you want to exchange for them,
you must book in advance.

129
00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:27,420
In Fengyang,

130
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,180
no one has made a booking yet.

131
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:30,340
Where is the coin?

132
00:08:33,460 --> 00:08:34,300
Here.

133
00:08:36,690 --> 00:08:38,140
Haven't you had any police training?

134
00:08:38,140 --> 00:08:40,180
I'm a veteran officer
with years of experience.

135
00:08:40,180 --> 00:08:41,500
I didn't touch it with my hands.

136
00:08:51,580 --> 00:08:54,140
Chief Liu, we haven't received
any reports in Fengyang

137
00:08:54,140 --> 00:08:55,980
regarding a missing woman lately.

138
00:08:55,980 --> 00:08:58,340
I've already sent people
to the mountains and the villages

139
00:08:58,340 --> 00:09:00,300
to ask around and see if there are any

140
00:09:00,300 --> 00:09:02,500
missing women under thirty-five.

141
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:05,660
How do you know

142
00:09:05,670 --> 00:09:07,300
it's a female under thirty-five?

143
00:09:07,300 --> 00:09:08,540
It's simple.

144
00:09:08,540 --> 00:09:09,780
Look at this.

145
00:09:09,780 --> 00:09:10,640
It is

146
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:12,380
the plastic sole of a shoe.

147
00:09:12,940 --> 00:09:14,300
This is a heel, and it's so small.

148
00:09:14,300 --> 00:09:16,380
This must be
from a thin high-heeled shoe.

149
00:09:16,380 --> 00:09:17,660
In Fengyang,

150
00:09:17,660 --> 00:09:19,460
those who wear these kinds of heels

151
00:09:19,460 --> 00:09:20,380
are generally

152
00:09:20,380 --> 00:09:21,740
women under thirty-five.

153
00:09:27,110 --> 00:09:27,950
What's this?

154
00:09:27,970 --> 00:09:29,140
A glass shard.

155
00:09:29,140 --> 00:09:31,520
For now, it's possible
that this shard slit the carotid artery.

156
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:32,980
We'll need to wait
for the lab results for details.

157
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:34,220
After the body is moved,

158
00:09:34,220 --> 00:09:36,980
sift through the surrounding soil again
to see if there are more like it.

159
00:09:36,980 --> 00:09:37,820
Understood, Chief Liu.

160
00:09:48,380 --> 00:09:49,460
Have some water.

161
00:09:49,460 --> 00:09:50,460
Thanks, Director Chen.

162
00:09:51,220 --> 00:09:53,060
The victim's carotid artery was slit.

163
00:09:53,060 --> 00:09:55,580
There are glass shards at the scene,
suspected to be the weapon.

164
00:09:56,060 --> 00:09:57,260
Yimei is reconstructing them.

165
00:09:58,740 --> 00:09:59,580
Right.

166
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,700
There are quite a few shards.

167
00:10:00,700 --> 00:10:01,740
They're being verified.

168
00:10:03,100 --> 00:10:04,300
The preliminary suspicion

169
00:10:04,300 --> 00:10:05,140
is homicide.

170
00:10:06,020 --> 00:10:07,460
- Master!
- We're confirming

171
00:10:07,460 --> 00:10:08,600
whether the coal gangue dump
was the primary crime scene.

172
00:10:12,820 --> 00:10:13,820
How's the search going?

173
00:10:13,820 --> 00:10:14,660
I checked

174
00:10:15,020 --> 00:10:17,900
no women are reported missing
across the 17 villages of Fengyang.

175
00:10:19,380 --> 00:10:20,300
Director Tong.

176
00:10:20,300 --> 00:10:22,020
Yimei, how's the reconstruction?

177
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:22,980
All processed, Chief Liu.

178
00:10:22,980 --> 00:10:23,900
Good.

179
00:10:23,900 --> 00:10:25,500
Hongbing,

180
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:28,380
get someone to take the body
to the municipal PSB for an autopsy.

181
00:10:28,380 --> 00:10:29,540
Alright. Limin,

182
00:10:29,540 --> 00:10:30,980
you go with Yimei.

183
00:10:30,980 --> 00:10:32,220
Help her carry the cases.

184
00:10:32,670 --> 00:10:34,140
- Let me help you.
- No need.

185
00:10:34,140 --> 00:10:35,420
- It's fine. It's heavy.
- Thank you.

186
00:10:35,420 --> 00:10:36,830
I'll head out first, Chief Liu.

187
00:10:36,830 --> 00:10:39,790
Tell them to investigate the coin
and the glass shards immediately.

188
00:10:39,790 --> 00:10:40,640
Alright, I've got it.

189
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:41,570
Go ahead.

190
00:10:41,590 --> 00:10:42,540
Stay safe.

191
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:44,980
Drive slowly on the road.

192
00:10:48,740 --> 00:10:50,300
This is the first big case

193
00:10:50,300 --> 00:10:52,300
in Fengyang in five years.

194
00:10:52,300 --> 00:10:53,980
We have to cooperate
with the municipal PSB

195
00:10:53,980 --> 00:10:55,600
and crack this case as soon as possible.

196
00:10:56,980 --> 00:10:57,820
Definitely.

197
00:10:59,820 --> 00:11:03,300
(Provide coal for the country,
contribute to Fengyang)

198
00:11:03,930 --> 00:11:04,780
Chief Liu,

199
00:11:04,780 --> 00:11:05,940
when you solve cases,

200
00:11:05,940 --> 00:11:07,660
(Fengyang Coal Mine Guesthouse)
where do you usually start?

201
00:11:07,660 --> 00:11:09,620
We'll first confirm
the victim's identity

202
00:11:09,620 --> 00:11:11,280
and then investigate
their social circle.

203
00:11:12,060 --> 00:11:13,820
The body was burned like that.

204
00:11:13,820 --> 00:11:14,820
It'll be hard to confirm

205
00:11:14,820 --> 00:11:15,860
their identity, right?

206
00:11:16,700 --> 00:11:17,780
What are your thoughts?

207
00:11:18,940 --> 00:11:20,940
Twenty-five years ago,

208
00:11:20,940 --> 00:11:22,100
on May 8,

209
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:24,260
a similar incident

210
00:11:24,280 --> 00:11:26,580
happened here in Fengyang.

211
00:11:26,580 --> 00:11:28,300
A young woman named Gao Ying

212
00:11:28,300 --> 00:11:30,460
was burned to death
at the coal gangue dump.

213
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,380
I believe these two cases

214
00:11:32,380 --> 00:11:33,660
were likely

215
00:11:33,660 --> 00:11:35,420
committed by the same killer.

216
00:11:36,540 --> 00:11:39,370
So do you think it should investigate
the case from 20 years ago?

217
00:11:39,370 --> 00:11:40,220
Of course.

218
00:11:40,220 --> 00:11:41,820
If we investigate two cases together,

219
00:11:41,820 --> 00:11:42,840
there will be

220
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:43,940
more clues.

221
00:11:44,580 --> 00:11:46,220
Wasn't the case solved back then?

222
00:11:46,220 --> 00:11:49,180
At the time, they thought it
was an industrial accident.

223
00:11:49,180 --> 00:11:50,020
But

224
00:11:50,020 --> 00:11:51,500
I think this case

225
00:11:51,500 --> 00:11:52,420
is suspicious.

226
00:11:52,700 --> 00:11:54,390
Then why didn't
you say so at the station?

227
00:11:56,060 --> 00:11:57,060
I just wanted to

228
00:11:57,060 --> 00:11:58,820
clear clues first.

229
00:11:58,820 --> 00:11:59,980
After all,

230
00:11:59,980 --> 00:12:02,260
this happened over 20 years ago.

231
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:03,820
Merging cases is no small matter.

232
00:12:03,820 --> 00:12:05,220
Let me think about it.

233
00:12:05,700 --> 00:12:07,220
What's there to think about?

234
00:12:07,220 --> 00:12:09,340
Report it to the leaders
at the municipal PSB.

235
00:12:09,340 --> 00:12:10,780
A quick phone call is all it takes.

236
00:12:11,140 --> 00:12:12,500
You can leave now.

237
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:13,620
We'll talk tomorrow.

238
00:12:14,780 --> 00:12:15,970
Alright, Chief Liu,

239
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:18,700
I'll go back and quickly organize
the materials.

240
00:12:18,700 --> 00:12:19,740
Let's strive

241
00:12:19,740 --> 00:12:20,820
to solve the case soon.

242
00:12:20,820 --> 00:12:21,780
It's settled then.

243
00:12:22,100 --> 00:12:22,940
Thank you.

244
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:24,340
Director Chen.

245
00:12:26,340 --> 00:12:27,260
See you tomorrow.

246
00:12:44,620 --> 00:12:46,260
What are you doing?

247
00:12:46,260 --> 00:12:48,560
You came back and just started digging
through everything here.

248
00:12:56,940 --> 00:12:58,220
I'm looking for my things.

249
00:13:00,660 --> 00:13:01,700
What are you looking for?

250
00:13:01,700 --> 00:13:03,780
Just tell me.

251
00:13:07,700 --> 00:13:08,780
If you rummage like this,

252
00:13:08,780 --> 00:13:10,180
everything will be a mess,

253
00:13:10,180 --> 00:13:11,860
and I won't be able to find anything.

254
00:13:13,860 --> 00:13:16,460
The candy box,

255
00:13:17,740 --> 00:13:20,540
the tin box with a little panda on it.

256
00:13:20,540 --> 00:13:22,140
Where was that?

257
00:13:24,860 --> 00:13:26,650
The one with Gao Ying's things, right?

258
00:13:33,860 --> 00:13:35,340
Did you drink at dinner tonight?

259
00:13:35,340 --> 00:13:36,260
Who drank?

260
00:13:36,260 --> 00:13:37,780
What makes you think I drank?

261
00:13:37,780 --> 00:13:39,860
If you didn't drink,
why are you acting crazy?

262
00:13:39,860 --> 00:13:40,780
Those things are from so many years ago.

263
00:13:40,780 --> 00:13:41,900
Why are you digging them up?

264
00:13:42,580 --> 00:13:43,520
It's official business.

265
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:45,420
Official business?

266
00:13:46,190 --> 00:13:47,860
Gao Ying has been gone
for over 20 years.

267
00:13:47,860 --> 00:13:49,990
Even if it's official business,
it should be settled by now.

268
00:13:50,220 --> 00:13:51,580
The municipal PSB wants to restart

269
00:13:51,590 --> 00:13:53,620
the investigation into
Gao Ying's cause of death.

270
00:13:53,620 --> 00:13:54,700
Is it the municipal PSB

271
00:13:54,700 --> 00:13:56,980
or is it you who wants to restart it?

272
00:13:56,980 --> 00:13:57,850
I'm a police officer.

273
00:13:57,850 --> 00:13:59,340
Isn't it the same thing?

274
00:13:59,340 --> 00:14:00,940
How can it be the same thing?

275
00:14:01,420 --> 00:14:02,460
We've only had a good life

276
00:14:02,460 --> 00:14:03,660
for a few years.

277
00:14:03,660 --> 00:14:05,260
Other families are moving forward.

278
00:14:05,260 --> 00:14:06,300
What are you doing?

279
00:14:06,300 --> 00:14:08,460
Do you drag me backward?

280
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:09,940
Stop being unreasonable.

281
00:14:09,940 --> 00:14:11,540
How am I being unreasonable?

282
00:14:11,540 --> 00:14:13,220
You're the one
acting crazy for no reason.

283
00:14:14,660 --> 00:14:16,700
Just tell me where that is!

284
00:14:16,700 --> 00:14:18,020
Come on.

285
00:14:18,020 --> 00:14:19,180
Go ask Hui.

286
00:14:23,060 --> 00:14:24,140
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)

287
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:29,740
♪Perhaps there are
too many things I don't understand♪

288
00:14:29,800 --> 00:14:30,670
Hello, Songge.

289
00:14:30,700 --> 00:14:31,620
- Songge.
- Lei,

290
00:14:31,620 --> 00:14:32,860
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)
you brought your friends here?

291
00:14:32,860 --> 00:14:33,800
Yeah, we just got here.

292
00:14:34,500 --> 00:14:35,340
Yan Jun,

293
00:14:35,340 --> 00:14:37,260
- go home early today.
- I know.

294
00:14:37,260 --> 00:14:39,340
Don't let your dad
catch you at the rink again.

295
00:14:39,340 --> 00:14:41,300
Be careful going in. Don't fall.

296
00:14:41,300 --> 00:14:42,780
Han Ning,

297
00:14:42,780 --> 00:14:44,460
I brought you some barbecue.

298
00:14:45,900 --> 00:14:48,060
When you're finished, you should rest.

299
00:14:48,060 --> 00:14:49,140
The shop can open anytime,

300
00:14:49,140 --> 00:14:50,180
but you only have one life.

301
00:14:50,700 --> 00:14:52,180
Thanks.

302
00:14:54,700 --> 00:14:55,940
Where did Chen Hui go?

303
00:14:58,380 --> 00:14:59,220
Over there.

304
00:15:01,420 --> 00:15:03,650
♪Don't break my heart♪

305
00:15:03,850 --> 00:15:05,960
♪Be gentle once again♪

306
00:15:06,230 --> 00:15:09,050
♪I don't want to see your silence♪

307
00:15:09,220 --> 00:15:10,100
Chen Hui.

308
00:15:10,930 --> 00:15:12,720
♪Waiting alone♪

309
00:15:13,420 --> 00:15:15,600
♪Enduring in silence♪

310
00:15:16,060 --> 00:15:16,900
Songge?

311
00:15:17,380 --> 00:15:18,220
You're back.

312
00:15:19,620 --> 00:15:21,580
Xing from the photo studio
ordered new costumes.

313
00:15:21,580 --> 00:15:22,860
I brought his catalog over.

314
00:15:22,860 --> 00:15:23,980
He wants us to take a look.

315
00:15:23,980 --> 00:15:25,180
Let's go see it together.

316
00:15:25,180 --> 00:15:26,020
Let's go.

317
00:15:26,980 --> 00:15:29,420
(A Terra-Cotta Warrior)

318
00:15:29,420 --> 00:15:30,900
Can you take a photo like this with me?

319
00:15:30,900 --> 00:15:33,180
A Terra-Cotta Warrior.

320
00:15:34,340 --> 00:15:35,940
This is my favorite movie.

321
00:15:37,540 --> 00:15:38,900
The movie is quite good,

322
00:15:38,900 --> 00:15:40,300
but the story is too tragic.

323
00:15:40,300 --> 00:15:42,020
The female lead dies in the end.

324
00:15:42,020 --> 00:15:43,420
After she died, she lived again.

325
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:44,540
Then she lived and died again.

326
00:15:44,540 --> 00:15:45,680
And finally, she lived again.

327
00:15:46,530 --> 00:15:47,400
Who is it?

328
00:15:47,420 --> 00:15:48,260
It's me.

329
00:15:48,620 --> 00:15:49,460
Hurry.

330
00:15:51,820 --> 00:15:52,660
Mr. Chen.

331
00:15:53,540 --> 00:15:55,140
- Dad.
- Hui.

332
00:15:55,140 --> 00:15:55,980
Songge,

333
00:15:56,420 --> 00:15:57,820
how has your health been lately?

334
00:15:57,820 --> 00:15:59,020
It's good.

335
00:16:00,020 --> 00:16:01,540
Dad, what's up?

336
00:16:01,540 --> 00:16:02,410
Did you see

337
00:16:02,420 --> 00:16:04,020
that iron box

338
00:16:04,020 --> 00:16:04,980
of mine?

339
00:16:04,980 --> 00:16:06,310
It's here with me.

340
00:16:06,320 --> 00:16:07,180
Find it for me quickly.

341
00:16:07,180 --> 00:16:08,020
I have a use for it.

342
00:16:08,030 --> 00:16:09,260
I know where it is. I'll go get it.

343
00:16:09,260 --> 00:16:10,100
Okay.

344
00:16:10,450 --> 00:16:11,300
It's under the drawer.

345
00:16:11,300 --> 00:16:12,140
Alright.

346
00:16:12,700 --> 00:16:14,620
Why are you touching
my things for no reason?

347
00:16:14,620 --> 00:16:16,860
Mom found it while she was cleaning.

348
00:16:16,860 --> 00:16:18,300
She's been nagging about it.

349
00:16:18,300 --> 00:16:19,780
So I brought it here quickly

350
00:16:19,780 --> 00:16:21,540
to keep her from getting upset.

351
00:16:22,500 --> 00:16:24,380
Tell me before you take things.

352
00:16:24,380 --> 00:16:25,420
You...

353
00:16:25,420 --> 00:16:27,340
It made me in a tough situation today.

354
00:16:27,780 --> 00:16:28,780
What happened?

355
00:16:28,780 --> 00:16:29,740
Did you

356
00:16:29,740 --> 00:16:30,580
have a fight at home?

357
00:16:31,540 --> 00:16:32,420
Your mother

358
00:16:32,420 --> 00:16:33,280
is unreasonable.

359
00:16:33,290 --> 00:16:34,380
Would I fight with her?

360
00:16:34,940 --> 00:16:35,980
Is it even worth it?

361
00:16:37,740 --> 00:16:38,580
Mr. Chen,

362
00:16:38,860 --> 00:16:39,700
is it this one?

363
00:16:40,060 --> 00:16:41,060
Yes.

364
00:16:41,620 --> 00:16:42,460
Good.

365
00:16:44,660 --> 00:16:45,500
Chief Liu.

366
00:16:48,500 --> 00:16:49,380
Who is it?

367
00:16:50,380 --> 00:16:52,780
I'm Yang Baichun,
manager of the guesthouse.

368
00:16:52,780 --> 00:16:54,500
Director Chen said you haven't had
something to eat.

369
00:16:54,500 --> 00:16:56,640
I had the kitchen
prepare something for you.

370
00:16:57,260 --> 00:16:58,100
One moment.

371
00:17:02,660 --> 00:17:03,540
Come in.

372
00:17:03,540 --> 00:17:05,540
I didn't know what you like to eat,

373
00:17:05,540 --> 00:17:06,860
so I just made a few things.

374
00:17:08,740 --> 00:17:10,940
If you need anything, just let me know.

375
00:17:10,940 --> 00:17:11,820
Thank you.

376
00:17:12,900 --> 00:17:13,740
Mr. Yang,

377
00:17:14,140 --> 00:17:15,580
I'd like to ask you about someone.

378
00:17:15,580 --> 00:17:16,980
Do you know someone named Gao Ying?

379
00:17:20,180 --> 00:17:21,540
Which Gao Ying?

380
00:17:21,550 --> 00:17:23,100
In 1972, the coal gangue dump
at your mine

381
00:17:23,100 --> 00:17:24,380
spontaneously combusted,

382
00:17:24,380 --> 00:17:25,520
and she was burned to death.

383
00:17:27,180 --> 00:17:28,100
I know her.

384
00:17:29,940 --> 00:17:32,580
She was a temporary worker
at our guesthouse.

385
00:17:33,180 --> 00:17:34,780
What happened to her back then?

386
00:17:35,220 --> 00:17:36,060
At that time,

387
00:17:36,060 --> 00:17:37,100
I had just started working.

388
00:17:37,100 --> 00:17:38,540
I wasn't very close to her.

389
00:17:39,620 --> 00:17:41,580
I was in charge of purchasing then.

390
00:17:41,580 --> 00:17:43,380
But I heard from others

391
00:17:43,380 --> 00:17:45,460
that she might have
been in a hurry that day.

392
00:17:45,460 --> 00:17:47,180
She took a shortcut home

393
00:17:47,180 --> 00:17:48,860
past the coal gangue,

394
00:17:48,860 --> 00:17:50,060
right when it caught fire.

395
00:17:50,060 --> 00:17:51,220
And she was gone.

396
00:17:51,220 --> 00:17:52,580
The coal gangue caught fire

397
00:17:52,580 --> 00:17:54,100
and burned a passerby to death.

398
00:17:54,100 --> 00:17:54,990
Is that normal?

399
00:17:55,740 --> 00:17:56,630
You don't know

400
00:17:56,630 --> 00:17:58,540
the area around that coal gangue

401
00:17:58,540 --> 00:17:59,540
is full of gas.

402
00:17:59,540 --> 00:18:00,740
As long as there's a tiny spark,

403
00:18:00,740 --> 00:18:02,220
it'll explode into a massive fireball,

404
00:18:02,220 --> 00:18:03,620
and people just get sucked right in.

405
00:18:03,620 --> 00:18:05,020
We have rules at the mine.

406
00:18:05,020 --> 00:18:07,740
If any kid goes there to play
and their parents find out,

407
00:18:07,740 --> 00:18:09,220
they'll get their legs broken at home.

408
00:18:10,660 --> 00:18:12,140
Does she have any family left?

409
00:18:12,820 --> 00:18:14,740
You'll have to ask Director Chen.

410
00:18:14,740 --> 00:18:17,300
Back then, Director Chen
was about to register their marriage.

411
00:18:18,140 --> 00:18:20,140
Director Chen? Chen Hongbing?

412
00:18:20,140 --> 00:18:21,100
That's right.

413
00:18:22,750 --> 00:18:24,670
Gao Ying was Chen Hongbing's fiancée?

414
00:18:25,180 --> 00:18:26,140
Yes.

415
00:18:38,980 --> 00:18:42,060
Dad, I'm going
to get the marriage certificate.

416
00:18:42,260 --> 00:18:47,260
(Year 1972)

417
00:18:50,740 --> 00:18:52,940
(Slow)

418
00:18:53,860 --> 00:18:55,740
(Civil Affairs Office, People's Committee
of Fengyang Town, Jiangbin City)

419
00:19:11,300 --> 00:19:12,740
You must be Huo Kaiming.

420
00:19:14,780 --> 00:19:16,100
I'm from the Security Department.

421
00:19:16,840 --> 00:19:17,720
What is it?

422
00:19:17,730 --> 00:19:19,140
The coal gangue dump caught fire,

423
00:19:19,140 --> 00:19:20,700
and it was my wife who burned to death.

424
00:19:21,100 --> 00:19:22,740
You were the attendant on duty then.

425
00:19:22,740 --> 00:19:23,620
Tell me

426
00:19:24,660 --> 00:19:26,980
how the coal gangue could
spontaneously combust.

427
00:19:26,980 --> 00:19:28,060
How could it combust?

428
00:19:29,580 --> 00:19:30,980
I don't know.

429
00:19:30,980 --> 00:19:32,900
What do you mean?

430
00:19:32,900 --> 00:19:34,900
- You were on duty and you don't know?
- They're fighting!

431
00:19:34,900 --> 00:19:35,810
Tell me how it combusted!

432
00:19:35,810 --> 00:19:36,650
Let go of me.

433
00:19:36,670 --> 00:19:37,580
Tell me how it combusted!

434
00:19:37,580 --> 00:19:38,820
- Let go!
- I won't!

435
00:19:38,820 --> 00:19:39,740
I don't know!

436
00:19:39,740 --> 00:19:40,580
I just don't know!

437
00:19:40,590 --> 00:19:42,380
Explain clearly how it combusted.

438
00:19:42,380 --> 00:19:43,580
I feel terrible that someone died too!

439
00:19:43,580 --> 00:19:46,140
Let go of me!

440
00:19:58,300 --> 00:20:02,020
(People's Public Security,
Jiangbin Municipal PSB)

441
00:20:08,910 --> 00:20:09,840
Chief Liu.

442
00:20:09,840 --> 00:20:10,780
- Director Chen.
- You're finally here.

443
00:20:10,780 --> 00:20:11,620
Look.

444
00:20:11,780 --> 00:20:13,300
I've found all the witnesses.

445
00:20:13,300 --> 00:20:14,760
They're just waiting
for your questioning.

446
00:20:14,940 --> 00:20:16,260
What witnesses?

447
00:20:16,820 --> 00:20:19,140
Witnesses for Gao Ying's case back then.

448
00:20:19,140 --> 00:20:21,980
These are all people
related to that incident.

449
00:20:21,980 --> 00:20:23,380
I didn't agree to investigate that.

450
00:20:25,100 --> 00:20:25,940
Chief Liu,

451
00:20:26,300 --> 00:20:28,060
let's just get
some background info first.

452
00:20:28,060 --> 00:20:29,460
Director Chen,

453
00:20:30,060 --> 00:20:30,900
I have already known

454
00:20:30,900 --> 00:20:32,620
about your relationship with Gao Ying.

455
00:20:36,380 --> 00:20:37,220
Chief Liu,

456
00:20:38,220 --> 00:20:39,060
let me tell you.

457
00:20:39,700 --> 00:20:41,420
After that incident happened back then,

458
00:20:41,420 --> 00:20:42,620
I felt something was wrong.

459
00:20:43,260 --> 00:20:45,140
Fengyang Mine
is a state-owned coal mine.

460
00:20:45,660 --> 00:20:46,580
The coal gangue dump

461
00:20:46,580 --> 00:20:48,460
has thorough safety regulations.

462
00:20:48,460 --> 00:20:50,420
How could it spontaneously
combust for no reason?

463
00:20:51,540 --> 00:20:53,940
And Gao Ying and I had plans that day.

464
00:20:53,940 --> 00:20:55,100
After she got off work,

465
00:20:55,300 --> 00:20:56,700
we were going
to the Civil Affairs Bureau.

466
00:20:56,700 --> 00:20:59,460
Why would she run off
to the coal gangue dump

467
00:20:59,460 --> 00:21:01,140
for no reason at all?

468
00:21:01,140 --> 00:21:02,160
Isn't this all a mystery?

469
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:04,860
I'm here to investigate
the body-burning case at Beimianling,

470
00:21:04,860 --> 00:21:06,580
not to solve your puzzles.

471
00:21:06,580 --> 00:21:07,580
Chief Liu,

472
00:21:08,660 --> 00:21:10,260
you agreed to it yesterday.

473
00:21:10,260 --> 00:21:11,100
Agreed to what?

474
00:21:12,100 --> 00:21:12,940
Look,

475
00:21:13,660 --> 00:21:14,980
didn't I say it yesterday?

476
00:21:14,980 --> 00:21:16,820
I said it is settled.

477
00:21:16,820 --> 00:21:18,020
And at the time,

478
00:21:18,020 --> 00:21:19,420
you didn't say a word.

479
00:21:19,420 --> 00:21:20,980
Currently, there's no evidence

480
00:21:20,980 --> 00:21:22,820
to show these two cases are linked.

481
00:21:22,820 --> 00:21:25,180
First, it might mislead
our investigation's direction.

482
00:21:25,180 --> 00:21:26,860
Second, it will drain our resources.

483
00:21:27,820 --> 00:21:29,620
So let's not waste time.

484
00:21:30,100 --> 00:21:31,500
Chief Liu,

485
00:21:31,500 --> 00:21:32,540
sorry.

486
00:21:32,540 --> 00:21:33,500
Look.

487
00:21:34,820 --> 00:21:35,660
I don't want candy.

488
00:21:36,460 --> 00:21:37,580
This isn't candy.

489
00:21:38,060 --> 00:21:40,060
This is a person's life.

490
00:21:40,060 --> 00:21:42,980
All the materials on
Gao Ying's case are right here.

491
00:21:42,980 --> 00:21:44,180
Let's talk about it.

492
00:21:44,180 --> 00:21:45,020
No need.

493
00:21:45,580 --> 00:21:47,020
Why can't you just say something?

494
00:21:47,020 --> 00:21:49,460
It doesn't cost anything to talk.

495
00:21:49,460 --> 00:21:51,260
Is it really that hard to communicate?

496
00:21:51,360 --> 00:21:52,580
Limin, let's start the meeting.

497
00:21:58,580 --> 00:21:59,740
Zhou.

498
00:22:00,340 --> 00:22:01,180
Wait a second.

499
00:22:03,540 --> 00:22:05,060
Let the witnesses go home. Dismissed.

500
00:22:05,300 --> 00:22:06,780
Everyone, you can go home now.

501
00:22:07,500 --> 00:22:08,540
Thanks.

502
00:22:08,540 --> 00:22:09,900
That's all for today.

503
00:22:09,900 --> 00:22:11,100
According to the forensics report
from the municipal PSB,

504
00:22:11,100 --> 00:22:12,980
it's confirmed
that the victim was killed

505
00:22:12,980 --> 00:22:14,660
(Weapon, glass shard)
by a glass shard to the carotid artery.

506
00:22:14,660 --> 00:22:16,500
Based on the reconstruction
of the shards,

507
00:22:16,500 --> 00:22:19,420
the shards are from
a Peidun Cough Syrup bottle.

508
00:22:19,420 --> 00:22:22,020
Peidun Cough Syrup
is produced overseas.

509
00:22:22,020 --> 00:22:23,210
Since it contains

510
00:22:23,220 --> 00:22:24,620
high levels of Kejianin,

511
00:22:24,620 --> 00:22:26,220
it is a banned substance in our country.

512
00:22:26,220 --> 00:22:27,380
(Peidun Cough Syrup)
Even overseas,

513
00:22:27,380 --> 00:22:28,900
it is strictly controlled.

514
00:22:28,900 --> 00:22:30,420
Since it's an overseas banned substance,

515
00:22:30,420 --> 00:22:33,340
how did it end up
in a small place like this?

516
00:22:33,340 --> 00:22:34,260
By the way,

517
00:22:34,260 --> 00:22:35,220
a while ago,

518
00:22:35,220 --> 00:22:37,900
the truck driver
involved in the accident

519
00:22:37,900 --> 00:22:38,980
supposedly said

520
00:22:38,980 --> 00:22:40,420
he'd had too much cough syrup.

521
00:22:40,420 --> 00:22:42,340
Then let's investigate
the syrup he drank.

522
00:22:42,340 --> 00:22:43,420
If it's the same brand,

523
00:22:43,420 --> 00:22:45,620
it means someone is selling it here.

524
00:22:45,620 --> 00:22:47,500
It could even be
a killing by a drug trafficking ring.

525
00:22:47,500 --> 00:22:48,740
A drug trafficking ring?

526
00:22:50,020 --> 00:22:50,860
Hongbing,

527
00:22:51,860 --> 00:22:52,740
what do you think?

528
00:22:52,740 --> 00:22:54,900
I think Chief Liu is right.

529
00:22:54,900 --> 00:22:55,740
There are

530
00:22:55,740 --> 00:22:57,780
a lot of migrant miners.

531
00:22:57,780 --> 00:22:59,740
The population is quite complex.

532
00:22:59,740 --> 00:23:01,380
All sorts of bad things can happen here.

533
00:23:01,380 --> 00:23:04,060
Even coal gangue
can spontaneously combust.

534
00:23:04,060 --> 00:23:06,140
What else couldn't happen?

535
00:23:06,140 --> 00:23:07,220
I think

536
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:08,870
interrogate the truck driver again.

537
00:23:09,500 --> 00:23:10,420
Confirm whether anyone

538
00:23:10,420 --> 00:23:12,780
is selling Peidun Cough Syrup
in Fengyang.

539
00:23:12,780 --> 00:23:14,740
That should at least
give us a starting point.

540
00:23:14,740 --> 00:23:15,700
Fine.

541
00:23:15,700 --> 00:23:16,660
Let's go with Chief Liu's plan.

542
00:23:16,660 --> 00:23:18,520
Hongbing, you go ahead and arrange it.

543
00:23:19,780 --> 00:23:22,140
Chief Liu

544
00:23:22,140 --> 00:23:23,740
and Limin

545
00:23:23,740 --> 00:23:25,860
will go to the detention center again

546
00:23:25,860 --> 00:23:28,340
to interrogate the guy
who drank the syrup.

547
00:23:29,300 --> 00:23:30,140
Chief Liu,

548
00:23:30,500 --> 00:23:32,060
does that arrangement work for you?

549
00:23:33,060 --> 00:23:33,940
That's fine.

550
00:23:33,940 --> 00:23:34,900
It's settled then.

551
00:23:34,900 --> 00:23:37,180
Also, we need to identify
the victim as soon as possible.

552
00:23:37,180 --> 00:23:38,420
Let's split up and investigate.

553
00:23:38,420 --> 00:23:40,140
Let's try to solve this case early.

554
00:23:44,620 --> 00:23:46,620
Dad, why did you bring
those things back again?

555
00:23:47,580 --> 00:23:48,740
Keep them safe for me for now.

556
00:23:48,740 --> 00:23:49,860
Don't lose them.

557
00:23:50,940 --> 00:23:53,020
Didn't they stop the investigation?

558
00:23:53,020 --> 00:23:54,060
How did you find out?

559
00:23:55,100 --> 00:23:56,300
Mr. Chen,

560
00:23:56,300 --> 00:23:57,380
we know.

561
00:23:57,380 --> 00:23:58,820
- Yeah, Mr. Chen, we all know.
- Right, we all know.

562
00:23:58,820 --> 00:23:59,780
Go ahead.

563
00:23:59,780 --> 00:24:00,740
You rascals.

564
00:24:01,960 --> 00:24:02,900
It's a family business.

565
00:24:02,900 --> 00:24:04,900
Don't go telling everyone everything.

566
00:24:07,780 --> 00:24:10,420
It's rare that I get off work this early.

567
00:24:10,420 --> 00:24:12,180
Play one of those

568
00:24:12,180 --> 00:24:13,020
good videos for me.

569
00:24:14,780 --> 00:24:15,620
Let's go.

570
00:24:37,780 --> 00:24:38,620
What time is it?

571
00:24:39,020 --> 00:24:40,300
Just past six.

572
00:24:44,420 --> 00:24:45,700
That was a good sleep.

573
00:24:45,700 --> 00:24:46,980
I feel refreshed.

574
00:24:48,380 --> 00:24:50,980
Dad, how long do you plan on hiding?

575
00:24:50,980 --> 00:24:52,940
I'm a police officer.

576
00:24:52,940 --> 00:24:53,780
Whom do I hide from?

577
00:24:54,540 --> 00:24:55,900
Hiding from Mom, obviously.

578
00:24:55,900 --> 00:24:56,820
In Fengyang,

579
00:24:56,820 --> 00:24:58,620
who else can handle you but her?

580
00:24:58,620 --> 00:25:00,060
Is it even a question?

581
00:25:06,580 --> 00:25:08,420
What happened today

582
00:25:09,660 --> 00:25:11,780
really caused quite a stir.

583
00:25:11,780 --> 00:25:13,900
Your mother definitely knows.

584
00:25:13,900 --> 00:25:15,690
I wanted to stay here for a bit.

585
00:25:16,780 --> 00:25:17,860
So you won't help me?

586
00:25:19,380 --> 00:25:20,220
Dad,

587
00:25:21,060 --> 00:25:22,220
don't blame me for it.

588
00:25:22,220 --> 00:25:23,740
It was all so long ago.

589
00:25:23,740 --> 00:25:24,740
Why can't you let it go?

590
00:25:25,060 --> 00:25:27,100
With all the noise you make every day,

591
00:25:27,100 --> 00:25:28,660
how do you think Mom feels?

592
00:25:29,260 --> 00:25:30,540
I'm a policeman.

593
00:25:31,340 --> 00:25:32,180
Investigating cases

594
00:25:32,180 --> 00:25:33,860
is my job.

595
00:25:33,860 --> 00:25:36,140
Regarding Gao Ying's matter,

596
00:25:36,140 --> 00:25:37,580
even though it's a cold case,

597
00:25:37,580 --> 00:25:39,460
as long as there's a chance,

598
00:25:40,060 --> 00:25:42,180
I still want to clear things up.

599
00:25:44,220 --> 00:25:45,820
Can you clear it up today?

600
00:25:45,820 --> 00:25:47,260
What do you mean?

601
00:25:47,260 --> 00:25:48,620
Go home, of course. What else?

602
00:25:48,620 --> 00:25:50,200
Do you really want to stay at my place?

603
00:25:53,140 --> 00:25:54,380
I guess you've grown up.

604
00:25:54,380 --> 00:25:56,220
You're already kicking me out.

605
00:25:56,220 --> 00:25:57,580
The groceries are ready.

606
00:25:57,580 --> 00:25:59,300
I'll go back with you
and have dinner with Mom.

607
00:26:00,060 --> 00:26:00,900
That's the spirit.

608
00:26:00,900 --> 00:26:02,940
You should have said so earlier.

609
00:26:02,940 --> 00:26:03,780
Let's go.

610
00:26:04,340 --> 00:26:06,540
Have you thought of how
to deal with your mother?

611
00:26:06,540 --> 00:26:07,700
Just one trick.

612
00:26:07,700 --> 00:26:08,780
What trick?

613
00:26:08,780 --> 00:26:10,140
Keep things worse.

614
00:26:10,140 --> 00:26:11,060
Brilliant.

615
00:26:11,060 --> 00:26:12,140
That's truly brilliant.

616
00:26:12,700 --> 00:26:13,940
Current News.

617
00:26:13,940 --> 00:26:16,300
Recently, in Beimianling of Fengyang,

618
00:26:16,300 --> 00:26:19,780
a murder and body disposal case
occurred in the coal gangue mountains.

619
00:26:19,780 --> 00:26:20,940
According to the investigation,

620
00:26:20,940 --> 00:26:22,100
- the victim was female,
- Checkmate.

621
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:24,820
aged approximately 30 to 35 years old.

622
00:26:24,820 --> 00:26:26,060
Because the body was charred,

623
00:26:26,060 --> 00:26:27,660
identification is difficult.

624
00:26:27,660 --> 00:26:28,500
Currently,

625
00:26:28,500 --> 00:26:30,860
the municipal criminal police are working
with the Fengyang Town station...

626
00:26:30,860 --> 00:26:32,340
I'm back.

627
00:26:32,340 --> 00:26:34,180
Why are you so late, Mom?

628
00:26:34,180 --> 00:26:36,820
You didn't tell me
you were coming back for dinner.

629
00:26:36,820 --> 00:26:38,300
If I'd known, I wouldn't have scheduled

630
00:26:38,300 --> 00:26:39,980
those last two patients.

631
00:26:39,980 --> 00:26:42,020
Dad asked me at the last minute.

632
00:26:42,020 --> 00:26:43,380
Welcome home, Ding Yue.

633
00:26:43,380 --> 00:26:45,340
Hui, bring Grandpa over to eat.

634
00:26:45,340 --> 00:26:46,700
The food is ready. Wash your hands.

635
00:26:47,740 --> 00:26:48,860
I'll wash my hands.

636
00:26:48,860 --> 00:26:49,940
Grandpa,

637
00:26:49,940 --> 00:26:50,880
time to eat.

638
00:26:51,060 --> 00:26:51,930
What?

639
00:26:52,300 --> 00:26:53,380
Fly a kite?

640
00:26:53,380 --> 00:26:54,860
It's so late.

641
00:26:54,860 --> 00:26:56,540
Your mom won't agree to it.

642
00:26:56,540 --> 00:26:58,180
Mom isn't home.

643
00:26:59,100 --> 00:27:00,940
- My mom isn't home.
- What?

644
00:27:00,940 --> 00:27:02,180
Why didn't you say so earlier?

645
00:27:02,180 --> 00:27:03,420
Let's go.

646
00:27:03,420 --> 00:27:04,420
Let's go fly a kite!

647
00:27:04,420 --> 00:27:05,260
Dad!

648
00:27:06,820 --> 00:27:08,020
Where are you going?

649
00:27:10,140 --> 00:27:11,180
Yeah, Grandpa.

650
00:27:11,180 --> 00:27:12,420
Where are you going?

651
00:27:12,420 --> 00:27:13,860
Didn't you say it's time to eat?

652
00:27:13,860 --> 00:27:16,500
Come on, let's eat.

653
00:27:17,180 --> 00:27:18,180
Are you

654
00:27:18,180 --> 00:27:19,420
trying to set me up?

655
00:27:22,080 --> 00:27:24,620
Hui, Grandpa is going for
a gastroscopy the day after tomorrow.

656
00:27:24,620 --> 00:27:26,100
Please go with him.

657
00:27:26,100 --> 00:27:27,620
The hospital is full of people you know.

658
00:27:27,620 --> 00:27:28,900
Would I even know
what's going on if I went?

659
00:27:28,900 --> 00:27:30,060
I'll go.

660
00:27:30,740 --> 00:27:32,000
Come on. Let's eat.

661
00:27:33,180 --> 00:27:35,260
Better let Hui take Grandpa.

662
00:27:35,260 --> 00:27:37,820
When he sees his old colleagues,
he will feel proud.

663
00:27:37,820 --> 00:27:38,660
Exactly.

664
00:27:38,660 --> 00:27:39,860
Let them have a look

665
00:27:39,860 --> 00:27:41,460
at my grandson.

666
00:27:42,100 --> 00:27:43,720
Fine, then I'll go.

667
00:27:43,940 --> 00:27:45,180
I'll let you stay home

668
00:27:45,180 --> 00:27:46,300
and have some alone time.

669
00:27:46,300 --> 00:27:47,860
What a good son.

670
00:27:47,860 --> 00:27:49,500
You're getting
more sensible, aren't you?

671
00:27:49,500 --> 00:27:50,460
Thanks.

672
00:27:53,420 --> 00:27:55,260
I heard Gao Ying's case

673
00:27:55,260 --> 00:27:56,580
isn't going smoothly.

674
00:28:05,220 --> 00:28:06,340
Mom,

675
00:28:06,340 --> 00:28:07,940
you're married to a policeman.

676
00:28:07,940 --> 00:28:09,740
You're sure prying into police business.

677
00:28:09,740 --> 00:28:10,580
Just eat.

678
00:28:11,820 --> 00:28:14,020
She has been with me
for most of her life.

679
00:28:14,020 --> 00:28:15,100
What doesn't she understand?

680
00:28:15,100 --> 00:28:16,660
She is just worried about me.

681
00:28:16,660 --> 00:28:17,620
You know?

682
00:28:19,700 --> 00:28:21,230
Let's not talk about work while we eat.

683
00:28:21,900 --> 00:28:23,980
Look at this,
steamed pork with rice flour.

684
00:28:23,980 --> 00:28:25,900
I made this especially for you today.

685
00:28:26,740 --> 00:28:27,580
Try it.

686
00:28:38,420 --> 00:28:40,820
Is salt free nowadays?

687
00:28:40,820 --> 00:28:42,580
It's salty?

688
00:28:42,580 --> 00:28:43,420
It shouldn't be.

689
00:28:43,440 --> 00:28:45,300
I was being careful.

690
00:28:47,700 --> 00:28:49,060
You call this salty?

691
00:28:49,060 --> 00:28:50,260
Being a doctor,

692
00:28:50,260 --> 00:28:51,460
your standards are way too high

693
00:28:51,460 --> 00:28:52,980
and too strict.

694
00:28:52,980 --> 00:28:54,820
Hui, give it a taste.

695
00:28:54,820 --> 00:28:56,220
Let me try.

696
00:29:01,850 --> 00:29:02,700
It's not salty.

697
00:29:02,700 --> 00:29:03,570
Look at this.

698
00:29:03,570 --> 00:29:04,540
It's quite tasty.

699
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:09,200
Mom, you should still be
the one cooking from now on.

700
00:29:18,820 --> 00:29:22,180
(Outpatient Department,
Jiangbin Municipal People's Hospital)

701
00:29:33,220 --> 00:29:34,720
Hey,

702
00:29:35,060 --> 00:29:36,540
let me ask you something.

703
00:29:36,540 --> 00:29:38,300
How long have you been on dialysis?

704
00:29:39,260 --> 00:29:40,420
Four years.

705
00:29:41,460 --> 00:29:42,620
What's up?

706
00:29:42,620 --> 00:29:43,820
How much have you cost for it

707
00:29:43,820 --> 00:29:45,940
in four years.

708
00:29:45,940 --> 00:29:47,420
I've only just started.

709
00:29:47,420 --> 00:29:49,420
One dialysis session costs over 300 yuan.

710
00:29:49,420 --> 00:29:51,380
It's such a money pit.

711
00:29:51,380 --> 00:29:53,060
When one person gets sick,

712
00:29:53,060 --> 00:29:55,740
it ruins the whole family.

713
00:30:01,020 --> 00:30:01,980
How are you?

714
00:30:01,980 --> 00:30:03,220
Feeling uncomfortable anywhere?

715
00:30:03,780 --> 00:30:04,980
No,

716
00:30:04,980 --> 00:30:06,060
everything's fine.

717
00:30:10,500 --> 00:30:12,240
Have Mr. and Mrs. Chen made up yet?

718
00:30:13,660 --> 00:30:15,130
They've stopped bickering, I suppose.

719
00:30:16,020 --> 00:30:17,060
Your hands are so cold.

720
00:30:17,060 --> 00:30:18,380
The hospital told me to notify you.

721
00:30:18,380 --> 00:30:21,060
A kidney donor for your elder sister
has been successfully matched.

722
00:30:21,060 --> 00:30:21,920
The next step

723
00:30:21,930 --> 00:30:23,420
is to proceed with the transplant.

724
00:30:23,420 --> 00:30:24,260
Wait here for a second.

725
00:30:24,280 --> 00:30:25,380
- I'll let the doctor see the report.
- Really?

726
00:30:25,380 --> 00:30:26,220
Yes.

727
00:30:26,700 --> 00:30:28,980
You need to prepare
the 300,000 yuan surgery fee first.

728
00:30:29,620 --> 00:30:30,860
After that,

729
00:30:30,860 --> 00:30:33,500
(Hemodialysis Room A)
follow the ward doctor's orders.

730
00:30:33,500 --> 00:30:35,220
It's not easy waiting
for a donor kidney.

731
00:30:36,380 --> 00:30:37,220
Thank you.

732
00:30:37,220 --> 00:30:38,060
Thank you so much.

733
00:30:38,080 --> 00:30:39,300
It's fine.

734
00:30:39,300 --> 00:30:40,820
- This is what we should do.
- Thank you.

735
00:30:40,820 --> 00:30:41,660
Go and tell her.

736
00:30:42,380 --> 00:30:43,220
Okay.

737
00:30:44,660 --> 00:30:45,940
Dr. Liu,

738
00:30:45,940 --> 00:30:47,860
these are Songge's test results.

739
00:30:47,860 --> 00:30:48,940
Please have a look.

740
00:30:50,060 --> 00:30:50,910
For now,

741
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:52,300
her condition is fairly stable.

742
00:30:52,300 --> 00:30:53,740
But in her situation,

743
00:30:53,740 --> 00:30:56,460
we generally recommend
a kidney transplant within two years.

744
00:30:56,460 --> 00:30:58,060
Otherwise, as she gets older,

745
00:30:58,060 --> 00:31:00,140
the risk of complications
will keep increasing.

746
00:31:01,020 --> 00:31:02,140
Look at these indicators.

747
00:31:02,140 --> 00:31:03,380
They aren't as good as before.

748
00:31:04,060 --> 00:31:05,020
Her daily diet

749
00:31:05,020 --> 00:31:06,580
must be strictly controlled.

750
00:31:06,580 --> 00:31:07,660
Keep a detailed food log.

751
00:31:07,660 --> 00:31:08,820
I've got it all in my notebook.

752
00:31:08,820 --> 00:31:09,660
Thank you, Doctor.

753
00:31:10,780 --> 00:31:11,620
Dr. Liu,

754
00:31:12,620 --> 00:31:14,340
is there still no donor kidney?

755
00:31:15,100 --> 00:31:16,780
We've been on the list for so long.

756
00:31:16,780 --> 00:31:18,340
Can you see if there's any way to help?

757
00:31:19,140 --> 00:31:21,220
I'll do anything you ask.

758
00:31:21,220 --> 00:31:23,300
All patients have to wait their turn.

759
00:31:23,300 --> 00:31:24,940
I've told you so many times.

760
00:31:24,940 --> 00:31:27,860
Once a suitable kidney is available,
we will notify you immediately.

761
00:31:28,260 --> 00:31:29,540
Go home and wait for news.

762
00:31:52,740 --> 00:31:53,700
Take your medicine.

763
00:31:53,700 --> 00:31:55,220
Thanks.

764
00:31:56,230 --> 00:31:57,420
You should get some sleep too.

765
00:32:01,660 --> 00:32:03,140
I want to tell you something.

766
00:32:03,140 --> 00:32:03,980
Go ahead.

767
00:32:06,180 --> 00:32:07,380
I think

768
00:32:08,260 --> 00:32:09,700
Hui and Songge

769
00:32:09,700 --> 00:32:10,700
are dating.

770
00:32:10,700 --> 00:32:11,780
You noticed too?

771
00:32:12,860 --> 00:32:14,300
I've felt it for a long time.

772
00:32:14,300 --> 00:32:16,060
But they won't admit it.

773
00:32:16,060 --> 00:32:17,220
How are we supposed to ask?

774
00:32:18,260 --> 00:32:20,180
Then we need to prepare in advance.

775
00:32:21,460 --> 00:32:22,300
Prepare for what?

776
00:32:22,780 --> 00:32:24,540
Wait, you really want Hui

777
00:32:24,540 --> 00:32:25,750
to be with Songge?

778
00:32:26,500 --> 00:32:27,620
When they are dating,

779
00:32:27,620 --> 00:32:29,180
can parents interfere?

780
00:32:29,180 --> 00:32:30,060
Songge

781
00:32:30,060 --> 00:32:31,460
is a sick child.

782
00:32:31,460 --> 00:32:33,100
If Hui stays with her,

783
00:32:33,100 --> 00:32:34,420
won't his life be over?

784
00:32:34,420 --> 00:32:36,060
Hui's skating rink

785
00:32:36,060 --> 00:32:37,220
is doing well.

786
00:32:37,220 --> 00:32:39,780
As for the dialysis money,
you don't have to worry too much.

787
00:32:39,780 --> 00:32:41,100
Besides,

788
00:32:41,100 --> 00:32:43,660
isn't Songge waiting for a donor kidney?

789
00:32:43,660 --> 00:32:45,300
Once the child gets a transplant,

790
00:32:45,300 --> 00:32:47,820
she'll be just like a normal person.

791
00:32:47,820 --> 00:32:50,140
But is a kidney really
that easy to wait for?

792
00:32:50,140 --> 00:32:51,000
Besides,

793
00:32:51,010 --> 00:32:52,220
the money from the skating rink

794
00:32:52,220 --> 00:32:53,500
is barely enough for dialysis.

795
00:32:53,500 --> 00:32:55,740
Your monthly salary
is only a few hundred bucks.

796
00:32:55,740 --> 00:32:57,380
That surgery costs over 300,000 yuan.

797
00:32:57,380 --> 00:32:58,740
Who does have the money

798
00:32:58,740 --> 00:33:00,820
for her transplant? You, I or Hui?

799
00:33:00,820 --> 00:33:02,290
What are you getting at? Just say it.

800
00:33:04,860 --> 00:33:06,380
Tomorrow,

801
00:33:06,380 --> 00:33:09,180
go find Hui and tell him to break up
with her as soon as possible.

802
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:11,700
No. Why don't you go do it yourself?

803
00:33:15,500 --> 00:33:16,460
Hello?

804
00:33:16,460 --> 00:33:17,900
Master, there's a new development

805
00:33:17,900 --> 00:33:19,020
in the Beimianling case.

806
00:33:19,020 --> 00:33:21,300
Director Tong said we should
have a meeting to go over it.

807
00:33:21,300 --> 00:33:22,300
Okay.

808
00:33:22,300 --> 00:33:23,220
I'll be right there.

809
00:33:23,260 --> 00:33:25,060
(Efficient and Pragmatic.
Fair and Honest)

810
00:33:25,700 --> 00:33:26,740
What's the situation?

811
00:33:27,500 --> 00:33:30,820
Master, Chief Liu and I went
to the detention center this morning.

812
00:33:30,820 --> 00:33:32,740
What the driver who caused
the accident drank wasn't

813
00:33:32,740 --> 00:33:33,780
regular cough syrup.

814
00:33:35,940 --> 00:33:37,500
(Peidun Cough Syrup)
Is this the cough syrup you drank?

815
00:33:38,820 --> 00:33:39,740
No.

816
00:33:39,740 --> 00:33:42,180
What I drank was a tube popsicle.

817
00:33:42,180 --> 00:33:43,620
The kind they sell on the street?

818
00:33:43,620 --> 00:33:44,940
No.

819
00:33:44,940 --> 00:33:46,640
This one was pretty expensive.

820
00:33:47,420 --> 00:33:48,780
30 yuan each.

821
00:33:48,780 --> 00:33:50,140
Don't play games with me.

822
00:33:50,140 --> 00:33:52,220
Who would buy
a tube popsicle for 30 yuan?

823
00:33:52,220 --> 00:33:53,260
Tell the truth.

824
00:33:53,900 --> 00:33:55,540
The guy told me

825
00:33:55,540 --> 00:33:57,700
it wasn't an ordinary tube popsicle.

826
00:33:57,700 --> 00:33:59,140
He filled them himself.

827
00:33:59,140 --> 00:33:59,980
There was

828
00:33:59,980 --> 00:34:00,980
cough syrup.

829
00:34:03,100 --> 00:34:05,140
He said it gives you a real rush.

830
00:34:05,140 --> 00:34:07,220
So I kept buying them from him.

831
00:34:07,900 --> 00:34:08,980
Where was the location?

832
00:34:08,980 --> 00:34:10,060
Over on the west side.

833
00:34:10,060 --> 00:34:12,420
At the gas station
by the suburban highway.

834
00:34:12,420 --> 00:34:13,900
He set up a stall there.

835
00:34:14,600 --> 00:34:16,940
Then why did you say
you just drank too much cough syrup?

836
00:34:17,940 --> 00:34:19,700
That's also what he told me to say.

837
00:34:19,700 --> 00:34:20,620
He said

838
00:34:20,620 --> 00:34:22,020
if anyone asked,

839
00:34:22,020 --> 00:34:22,860
just say I drank

840
00:34:22,860 --> 00:34:25,100
too much cough syrup
I bought at a pharmacy.

841
00:34:25,100 --> 00:34:26,620
What was the person's name?

842
00:34:26,620 --> 00:34:27,620
What did he look like?

843
00:34:27,620 --> 00:34:28,940
His name was

844
00:34:29,820 --> 00:34:30,820
Lu Yuan.

845
00:34:31,620 --> 00:34:32,500
It's hard to say

846
00:34:32,500 --> 00:34:33,740
what he looked like.

847
00:34:33,740 --> 00:34:35,140
He always wore

848
00:34:35,140 --> 00:34:37,220
a dark red hat and a mask.

849
00:34:37,220 --> 00:34:39,060
He pulled the brim down very low,

850
00:34:39,060 --> 00:34:40,540
showing only his eyes.

851
00:34:40,540 --> 00:34:41,740
I couldn't see his face.

852
00:34:42,940 --> 00:34:46,060
Can we confirm Lu Yuan's real identity?

853
00:34:46,060 --> 00:34:47,300
We checked.

854
00:34:47,300 --> 00:34:48,260
In our town,

855
00:34:48,260 --> 00:34:49,500
there are seven people

856
00:34:49,500 --> 00:34:50,420
registered as Lu Yuan.

857
00:34:50,420 --> 00:34:52,220
One of them has already passed away.

858
00:34:52,220 --> 00:34:53,620
Two are over 70 years old.

859
00:34:53,620 --> 00:34:55,300
As for the other five, none of them

860
00:34:55,300 --> 00:34:57,340
(Resident Identity Card)
match the truck driver's description.

861
00:34:57,340 --> 00:34:58,220
So I suspect

862
00:34:58,220 --> 00:34:59,220
that Lu Yuan

863
00:34:59,220 --> 00:35:00,300
is a fake name.

864
00:35:00,300 --> 00:35:01,460
Did you go to the gas station?

865
00:35:01,460 --> 00:35:02,420
People there said

866
00:35:02,420 --> 00:35:04,140
Lu Yuan did have a small stall,

867
00:35:04,140 --> 00:35:05,790
but he hasn't shown up
for the last two days.

868
00:35:05,820 --> 00:35:08,220
This cough syrup is addictive.

869
00:35:08,220 --> 00:35:09,060
The truck driver

870
00:35:09,070 --> 00:35:11,340
drank it and that's
what caused the accident.

871
00:35:11,340 --> 00:35:13,580
We must quickly find
the source of these sales.

872
00:35:14,580 --> 00:35:16,500
But we only have information

873
00:35:16,500 --> 00:35:18,180
on this one seller, Lu Yuan.

874
00:35:18,180 --> 00:35:20,340
Whether the source is

875
00:35:20,340 --> 00:35:21,300
is hard to say.

876
00:35:21,300 --> 00:35:23,460
Only by finding this Lu Yuan

877
00:35:23,460 --> 00:35:25,220
can we get the next breakthrough.

878
00:35:25,220 --> 00:35:26,300
What about this?

879
00:35:26,300 --> 00:35:27,300
Investigate from both

880
00:35:27,300 --> 00:35:28,380
the sellers

881
00:35:28,380 --> 00:35:29,530
and the buyers.

882
00:35:29,530 --> 00:35:30,390
During the day,

883
00:35:30,390 --> 00:35:32,340
I can head into town and look around.

884
00:35:32,340 --> 00:35:33,660
(People's Public Security)
I'll see if they're selling those

885
00:35:33,660 --> 00:35:35,340
(Fengyang Town Police Station, Jiangbin Municipal PSB)
twenty or thirty-yuan tube popsicles.

886
00:35:35,340 --> 00:35:36,300
I'll also ask around

887
00:35:36,300 --> 00:35:38,100
to see if anyone has seen Lu Yuan.

888
00:35:38,100 --> 00:35:39,260
At night,

889
00:35:39,260 --> 00:35:40,380
we will organize

890
00:35:40,380 --> 00:35:41,820
a surprise nighttime inspection.

891
00:35:41,820 --> 00:35:42,660
Anyone

892
00:35:42,660 --> 00:35:44,300
who tests positive for Kejianin

893
00:35:44,300 --> 00:35:45,220
will definitely

894
00:35:45,220 --> 00:35:46,940
be linked to this gang.

895
00:35:46,980 --> 00:35:49,460
(Bear Cub Tube Popsicles)

896
00:35:49,810 --> 00:35:50,660
This way.

897
00:35:50,660 --> 00:35:51,500
Let's go.

898
00:35:52,740 --> 00:35:53,580
Master,

899
00:35:54,210 --> 00:35:56,450
we caught five people
who were using the tube popsicles.

900
00:35:56,880 --> 00:35:57,740
Take them back.

901
00:35:57,740 --> 00:35:59,220
Hurry up and take their statements.

902
00:35:59,540 --> 00:36:00,660
And see if you can

903
00:36:00,660 --> 00:36:02,860
track down the supplier
of these tube popsicles.

904
00:36:02,860 --> 00:36:03,700
Got it.

905
00:36:07,060 --> 00:36:08,100
(Did you talk to Hui?)

906
00:36:08,100 --> 00:36:09,540
I can't go back with you.

907
00:36:09,540 --> 00:36:10,420
I have something to do.

908
00:36:10,420 --> 00:36:11,260
What's up?

909
00:36:12,260 --> 00:36:14,220
Just do your own job well.

910
00:36:14,220 --> 00:36:15,060
Sure.

911
00:36:17,900 --> 00:36:19,860
(Entertainment.
Endless fun all day long)

912
00:36:24,900 --> 00:36:25,740
Dad.

913
00:36:27,580 --> 00:36:28,420
Where's Songge?

914
00:36:28,860 --> 00:36:30,300
She went to the city for dialysis.

915
00:36:30,300 --> 00:36:31,660
What's wrong? What's going on?

916
00:36:31,660 --> 00:36:32,500
Let me get you a drink.

917
00:36:32,500 --> 00:36:34,260
It's fine. Don't bother.

918
00:36:35,820 --> 00:36:38,620
There are a few important things
I need to tell you.

919
00:36:38,620 --> 00:36:39,660
What?

920
00:36:39,660 --> 00:36:40,580
Your mom

921
00:36:40,580 --> 00:36:41,780
is busy right now,

922
00:36:41,780 --> 00:36:43,580
so she asked me to talk to you.

923
00:36:44,420 --> 00:36:45,860
I'm mainly here to tell you

924
00:36:45,860 --> 00:36:46,700
about you and...

925
00:36:46,700 --> 00:36:48,300
Is this about Songge and me?

926
00:36:50,460 --> 00:36:51,580
With something this big,

927
00:36:52,420 --> 00:36:54,020
as the head of the household,

928
00:36:54,020 --> 00:36:55,460
shouldn't I be allowed

929
00:36:55,460 --> 00:36:56,460
to ask about it?

930
00:36:58,140 --> 00:36:59,380
Are you and Songge

931
00:37:00,100 --> 00:37:01,220
really in a relationship?

932
00:37:02,740 --> 00:37:03,860
You're a policeman,

933
00:37:03,860 --> 00:37:04,860
so did you just notice?

934
00:37:05,380 --> 00:37:06,220
What's the matter?

935
00:37:06,820 --> 00:37:08,060
Is Mom unhappy?

936
00:37:08,060 --> 00:37:09,820
You should understand

937
00:37:09,820 --> 00:37:11,540
what your mother means.

938
00:37:11,540 --> 00:37:12,620
It's all for your own good,

939
00:37:12,620 --> 00:37:13,460
isn't it?

940
00:37:15,060 --> 00:37:15,900
Dad,

941
00:37:16,300 --> 00:37:17,420
what's your stance?

942
00:37:17,420 --> 00:37:18,740
I don't have a stance.

943
00:37:18,740 --> 00:37:20,940
I just want to tell you

944
00:37:20,940 --> 00:37:22,900
that every parent

945
00:37:22,900 --> 00:37:23,980
hopes their child

946
00:37:23,980 --> 00:37:24,820
lead a good life.

947
00:37:25,820 --> 00:37:28,500
Getting married and starting a family
are major life events.

948
00:37:29,180 --> 00:37:30,460
Your mother and I

949
00:37:31,220 --> 00:37:33,420
have to look out for your future.

950
00:37:33,420 --> 00:37:34,260
Dad,

951
00:37:34,260 --> 00:37:36,260
it's impossible for me to leave Songge.

952
00:37:38,500 --> 00:37:39,980
No one is forcing you to leave.

953
00:37:40,580 --> 00:37:41,740
But I have to tell you

954
00:37:41,740 --> 00:37:43,100
if you're going to be with her,

955
00:37:44,700 --> 00:37:46,380
you need to be mentally prepared.

956
00:37:46,380 --> 00:37:47,580
I am prepared.

957
00:37:47,580 --> 00:37:48,960
I'll just work hard to make money.

958
00:37:49,300 --> 00:37:51,980
Once she gets a kidney transplant,
she'll be just like anyone else.

959
00:37:51,980 --> 00:37:53,260
Anyway, I'm telling you

960
00:37:54,020 --> 00:37:55,740
I've already conveyed

961
00:37:55,740 --> 00:37:56,940
your mother's and my opinion.

962
00:37:57,740 --> 00:37:59,780
You think it over carefully.

963
00:38:05,420 --> 00:38:07,260
You sell tube popsicles here too?

964
00:38:09,340 --> 00:38:10,180
I'd have one.

965
00:38:11,100 --> 00:38:13,180
You're too old to be eating these.

966
00:38:13,180 --> 00:38:14,820
I just saw everyone else eating them

967
00:38:15,380 --> 00:38:17,060
(Bear Cub Tube Popsicles)
and wondered what they tasted like.

968
00:38:17,060 --> 00:38:17,900
How do you open it?

969
00:38:18,660 --> 00:38:19,620
Let me open it for you.

970
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:28,220
Have you seen anyone selling these
at stalls on the street?

971
00:38:28,220 --> 00:38:29,500
Aren't they sold everywhere?

972
00:38:30,180 --> 00:38:32,500
I mean the ones that cost 30 yuan each.

973
00:38:33,140 --> 00:38:34,300
30 yuan?

974
00:38:34,980 --> 00:38:36,820
I sell only one-fifty each.

975
00:38:36,820 --> 00:38:38,340
30? That's crazy.

976
00:38:38,340 --> 00:38:39,500
Forget it.

977
00:38:39,500 --> 00:38:41,250
Even if I told you,
you wouldn't understand.

978
00:38:42,820 --> 00:38:44,420
Think carefully about what I told you.

979
00:38:45,060 --> 00:38:46,090
- I know.
- I'm off.

980
00:38:53,780 --> 00:38:57,580
(Bear Cub Tube Popsicles)

981
00:39:20,980 --> 00:39:22,220
My dad knows.

982
00:39:22,220 --> 00:39:23,220
Stop the transaction.

983
00:39:36,850 --> 00:39:42,950
♪I always thought
once we see the full picture♪

984
00:39:44,270 --> 00:39:50,090
♪We could understand
each other with empathy♪

985
00:39:51,680 --> 00:39:58,100
♪I always thought
the path we never took♪

986
00:39:58,830 --> 00:40:04,420
♪Must have had more beautiful scenery♪

987
00:40:06,270 --> 00:40:09,640
♪Keep moving forward
and don't look back♪

988
00:40:09,980 --> 00:40:13,230
♪The shore is only reached
by the road ahead♪

989
00:40:13,640 --> 00:40:16,490
♪Too much debt has accumulated♪

990
00:40:17,380 --> 00:40:20,280
♪In this short life♪

991
00:40:21,050 --> 00:40:24,700
♪Between right and wrong,
how to choose?♪

992
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:28,260
♪Regret is inevitable in the end♪

993
00:40:28,420 --> 00:40:35,060
♪Even so-called love
is repaid with pain♪

994
00:40:35,560 --> 00:40:39,510
♪I hear the laughter
and follow the crowd♪

995
00:40:39,710 --> 00:40:42,930
♪Into the streets and alleys♪

996
00:40:43,180 --> 00:40:50,030
♪On that brightly lit night♪

997
00:40:50,750 --> 00:40:54,320
♪Unfortunately, the breeze in town♪

998
00:40:54,510 --> 00:40:58,050
♪Can no longer catch up to the children♪

999
00:40:58,050 --> 00:41:01,190
♪Times have changed♪

1000
00:41:01,600 --> 00:41:04,000
♪Now, everything♪

1001
00:41:04,660 --> 00:41:08,840
♪Is no longer what it used to be♪

